title: Transformers Cybertronian Index
description:
The Cybertronian Index is a complete listing of all Transformers released from Generation 1 through Robots in Disguise.  This publication differs from the previous Recognition Guides as it doesn't go into detail on each figure, but only shows the basic transformations.  Since some of the pictures were very small, I scanned the pages with a higher resolution, hence the larger file size.
 To my knowledge, The Index is the last Transformers book released by Antarctic Press to be scanned and uploaded.
 Enjoy!
